==Remakes==
In June 2012, [[Microïds]] ([[Anuman Interactive]]’s adventure game label) released '''''The Bluecoats: North vs South''''',<ref>[http://ifanzine.com/the-bluecoats-north-vs-south-review/ The Bluecoats: North vs. South Review on iFanzine]</ref> a [[Video game remake|remake]] for iOS and Android compatible devices<ref>[http://www.ign.com/games/the-bluecoats-north-vs-south/iphone-134401 The Bluecoats: North vs. South on IGN.com]</ref> and for Windows.<ref>[http://www.gamespot.com/the-bluecoats-north-and-south/platform/pc/ The Bluecoats: North & South for PC on ''GameSpot'']</ref>
The iOS version received a metascore of 60 on [[Metacritic]].<ref>[https://archive.today/20130129154831/http://www.metacritic.com/game/ios/the-bluecoats---north-vs-south/critic-reviews The Bluecoats – North vs South iOS on metacritic.com]</ref>
