Another remake, titled '''''North & South: The Game''''', was released for iOS on November 6, 2012 by bitComposer Entertainment AG<ref>[https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/north-south-the-game/id512958666?mt=8 North & South: The Game for iOS on iTunes]</ref>

